01:20:53,537 --> 01:20:57,462
Entahlah, aku milik
Vietnam, aku bilang padamu.

1071
01:20:57,641 --> 01:20:59,871
Boleh aku memilih LBJ?

1072
01:21:01,412 --> 01:21:04,904
